OL,3,CStrictly star teaches salsa steps to
OL,4,Cprimary school pupils
OL,6,FAround 100 pupils at a Guernsey
OL,7,Fprimary school were treated to a
OL,8,Fdancing class by Strictly Come
OL,9,FDancing's Kai Widdrington.
OL,11,FThe professional, who dances in front
OL,12,Fof millions of viewers every Saturday,
OL,13,Ftaught salsa steps to pupils at
OL,14,FAmherst Primary School - something he
OL,15,Fsays is a lot scarier than what he's
OL,16,Fused to.
