OL,3,CStrictly star teaches salsa steps to
OL,4,Cprimary school pupils
OL,6,FKai says: "We dance in front of 10-12
OL,7,Fmillion people every week on the telly
OL,8,Fbut I get more nervous doing this sort
OL,9,Fof thing because they're right there
OL,10,Fin front of you and kids can ask you
OL,11,Fanything and anything can happen."
OL,13,FAs well as teaching the kids some
OL,14,Fmoves, Widdrington also performed the
OL,15,FCharleston and took questions from
OL,16,Fpupils and teachers.
OL,18,FKai explains: "It's just an amazing
OL,19,Fthing for kids to get into and I think
OL,20,Fif you get them at that young age, it
OL,21,Freally sparks that interest.
