OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F389A1728595436
OL,3,CStrictly star teaches salsa steps to
OL,4,Cprimary school pupils
OL,6,F"I'm hoping some of them will think 'I
OL,7,Fwatched him on Strictly, he started
OL,8,Fwhen he was 7 and grew up just over
OL,9,Fthe water in Southampton, so why can't
OL,10,FI do it.'"
OL,12,FThe Strictly star was on the island to
OL,13,Fhelp promote the Guernsey
OL,14,FInternational DanceSport Championships
OL,15,Fdue to be held in December at the Beau
OL,16,FSejour Leisure Centre.
OL,18,FThe British Dance Sport Association,
OL,19,Fwhich is organising the event, hopes
OL,20,Fthere will be around 500 competitors.
