OL,3,CStrictly star teaches salsa steps to
OL,4,Cprimary school pupils
OL,6,FPeter Nash, the organisation's Sport
OL,7,Fand Development Director, said:
OL,8,F"Guernsey is a very sporty island. The
OL,9,Fisland does brilliantly for somewhere
OL,10,Fso small.
OL,12,F"It's also got such a rich history
OL,13,Fwith dancing too, stretching all the
OL,14,Fway back to the 1980s.
OL,16,F"I remember coming to events here
OL,17,Fwhere there were competitions in car
OL,18,Fparks. So, it's brilliant to come back
OL,19,Fhere again."
